sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Root as Root Agent
    participant Sim as LoanSimulationAgent
    participant Eval as PackageEvaluatorAgent
    participant Calc as Calculator API
    participant State as Session State

    User->>Root: "Simulate a 60/40 split package"
    Root->>State: Read user_profile, loan_initial_results
    Root->>Root: Call simulate_loan_tracks wrapper

    activate Sim
    Root->>Sim: track_specifications, tool_context
    Sim->>Sim: Create internal session
    loop For each track
        Sim->>Calc: calculateLoan(track params)
        Calc-->>Sim: calculation result + GUID
    end
    Sim->>Sim: Compute weighted averages
    Sim->>State: Write proposed_packages[package_id]
    Sim->>State: Write amortization_artifacts[guid]
    Sim-->>Root: MortgagePackage result
    deactivate Sim

    User->>Root: "Evaluate this package"
    Root->>State: Read proposed_packages[package_id]
    Root->>Root: Call evaluate_mortgage_package wrapper

    activate Eval
    Root->>Eval: mortgage_package, evaluation_criteria
    Eval->>Eval: Create internal session
    Eval->>Eval: Assess risk, affordability, cost
    Eval->>State: Write package_evaluations[eval_id]
    Eval-->>Root: PackageEvaluation result
    deactivate Eval

    Root-->>User: Recommendation with scores
